cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper proposes a neural network-based method for point cloud registration, which involves computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG) techniques. The method also involves solving rigid body motion, which falls under robotics (RO) and artificial intelligence (AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with geometric features, which is related to computational geometry (GR). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.RO, cs.AI, and cs.GR.
